  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to KDNSSD</title>

    <para>
      The <application>KDNSSD</application> package contains a library
      for handling the DNS-based Service Discovery Protocol (DNS-SD).
    </para>

    &lfs77_checked;

